    public class RecurrenceRule
extends PropertyBase<RecurrenceRule2,RecurrenceRule>

    RRULE Recurrence Rule RFC 5545 iCalendar 3.8.5.3, page 122.

    This property defines a rule or repeating pattern for recurring events, to-dos, journal entries, or time zone definitions.

    Produces a stream of start date/times after applying all modification rules.

    See Also:
    VEvent, VTodo, VJournal, DaylightSavingTime, StandardTime
